<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Skilless" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Skilless</orth> or <orth extent="full" opt="n">Skillless,</orth> inexpert, ignorant: <bibl n="shak. tro 1.1.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 1, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.3.132" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 3, 132</bibl>. With <emph>in</emph>: <cit><quote>being s. in these parts,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 3.3.9" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 3, 9</bibl></cit> (unacquainted with this country). With <emph>of</emph>: <cit><quote>how features are abroad, I am s. of,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.1.53" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. III, 1, 53</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>